<table width="auto"  border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0"><tr><td colspan=3>House Bill/Resolution NO. <b>HB04309</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>FULL TITLE : AN ACT INSTITUTING POLICIES TO MITIGATE THE TRAFFIC CRISIS IN THE COUNTRY AND FOR OTHER PURPOSES</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>SHORT TITLE : Traffic Mitigating Act</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>ABSTRACT : Grants emergency powers to the President in order to bring forth solutions, either short or long term to the perennial problem of traffic congestion, not just in Metro Manila but also of the whole country which drains time and resources of the nation.</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>PRINCIPAL AUTHOR/S : <b>ROBES, FLORIDA &quot;RIDA&quot; P.</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>DATE FILED : 2016-11-08</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>SIGNIFICANCE: NATIONAL</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3><b>ACTIONS TAKEN BY THE COMMITTEE</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>MOTHER BILL:&nbspHB06425</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3><b>ACTIONS TAKEN BY THE COMMITTEE ON RULES</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>REFERRAL TO THE COMMITTEE ON TRANSPORTATION ON 2016-11-14</td></tr></table>